---
title: Quick Sausage Meat and Mash with Onion Gravy and Peas
description: Pub fare at its finest! Our speedy take on sausage and mash uses Italian sausage meat for maximum flavour with minimal effort, paired with creamy mash and doused in a sweet-and-savoury onion gravy.
